@Akshita Purohit Hi Akshita,
Is it just the Lambda console that does not load? Is it the home page of the Lambda console, or is it the page for creating functions?
I did not meet with this issue before, but here’s what I would try:
1, If using IAM user to log in, see if permission is right and lambda permission is granted (although you should usually see an unauthorized alert instead of a blank page);
2, Try logging in using the root account if the IAM user does not work;
3, Submit an AWS support request on the management console and see what AWS support says. 
Hope this helps!
